                <td class="p-2 font-mono">IC<sub>12</sub> = &radic;(IC<sub>1</sub> &middot; IC<sub>2</sub>)</td>
                <td class="p-2 text-blue-400">Geometric</td>
                <td class="p-2 font-mono text-kernel-600">I-C3</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-kernel-800">
                <td class="p-2 font-mono text-purple-400">C</td>
                <td class="p-2">Does not compose</td>
                <td class="p-2 text-kernel-600">None</td>
                <td class="p-2 font-mono text-kernel-600">I-E7</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 font-mono text-yellow-400">&Delta;</td>
                <td class="p-2 font-mono">&Delta;<sub>12</sub> = (&Delta;<sub>1</sub>+&Delta;<sub>2</sub>)/2 + (&radic;IC<sub>1</sub>&minus;&radic;IC<sub>2</sub>)&sup2;/2</td>
                <td class="p-2 text-yellow-400">Hellinger-like</td>
                <td class="p-2 font-mono text-kernel-600">I-D9</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════ §9: FIXED POINTS & FISHER METRIC ═══════════ -->
    <section id="fixed-points" class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-kernel-100 mb-4">Fixed Points &amp; Fisher Metric</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <!-- Fixed Points -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-kernel-300 mb-3">Geodesic Partition <span class="text-kernel-600 font-normal">(I-D11)</span></h3>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-kernel-300 font-bold">&varepsilon; = 10<sup>&minus;8</sup></span>
                <span class="text-kernel-600">&theta;/&pi; &asymp; 0</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">Guard boundary &mdash; no channel fully dies</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-red-800/30 rounded p-3 text-xs">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">c<sub>trap</sub> = 0.3177</span>
                <span class="text-kernel-600">&theta;/&pi; = 0.191</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">&Gamma;(&omega;<sub>trap</sub>) = 1 &mdash; trapping threshold (Cardano root)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-amber-800/30 rounded p-3 text-xs">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-amber-400 font-bold">c = &frac12;</span>
                <span class="text-kernel-600">&theta;/&pi; = 0.250</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">Equator &mdash; max entropy, S + &kappa; = 0 (quintuple fixed point)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-900 border border-cyan-800/30 rounded p-3 text-xs">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold">c* = 0.7822</span>
                <span class="text-kernel-600">&theta;/&pi; = 0.354</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">Self-dual &mdash; maximizes S + &kappa; per channel</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-kernel-300 font-bold">c &asymp; 1</span>
                <span class="text-kernel-600">&theta;/&pi; &asymp; 0.5</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">Perfect fidelity &mdash; upper clamp</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Fisher Metric -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-kernel-300 mb-3">Fisher Metric Results</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs">
              <span class="text-kernel-300 font-bold">g<sub>F</sub>(c)</span>
              <div class="font-mono text-purple-300 mt-1">g<sub>F</sub>(c) = 1 / [c(1 &minus; c)]</div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">Fisher metric in c-parameterization</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs">
              <span class="text-kernel-300 font-bold">g<sub>F</sub>(&theta;)</span>
              <div class="font-mono text-blue-300 mt-1">g<sub>F</sub>(&theta;) = 1 (flat!)</div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">Manifold is flat in Fisher coordinates &mdash; all structure from embedding</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs">
              <span class="text-kernel-300 font-bold">Fano-Fisher</span>
              <div class="font-mono text-green-300 mt-1">h''(c) = &minus;g<sub>F</sub>(c)</div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">Entropy curvature IS the Fisher metric (I-A3)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs">
              <span class="text-kernel-300 font-bold">&int; g<sub>F</sub>&middot;S</span>
              <div class="font-mono text-amber-300 mt-1">&int;<sub>0</sub><sup>1</sup> g<sub>F</sub>(c) &middot; S(c) dc = &pi;&sup2;/3</div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 mt-1">= 2&zeta;(2) &mdash; the Basel constant (I-B7)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs">
              <span class="text-kernel-300 font-bold">Rank Classification</span>
              <div class="font-mono text-cyan-300 mt-1 space-y-0.5">
                <p>Rank-1: all c<sub>i</sub>=c<sub>0</sub> &rarr; IC=F, C=0 (1 DOF)</p>
                <p>Rank-2: 2-channel &rarr; IC=&radic;(F&sup2;&minus;C&sup2;/4) (2 DOF)</p>
                <p>Rank-3: general &rarr; F, &kappa;, C independent (3 DOF)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════ §10: BUILDER ═══════════ -->
